column1: event,"I think I have ruined my life. I officially hate myself. I hate so many things about me. I am so ugly and annoying, I don't know what is wrong with me. Ugh. What is wrong with me. Damn!"
event,"I read Raquel's journal and it made my day. I love her.

It makes me angry, how people are so dismissive to Hannah.  They never give her the time of day.  And if they actually sat down and talked with her, they would realize how smart and insightful she actually is.  She isn't stupid, she knows how people talk behind her back.  And in Civ, for the Renaissance art projects, no one went to hers.  It was so incredibly rude.  Yeah, she's got problems, and issues, but so does everyone else in the grade.  She is just the only who is honest about her feelings, unlike myself when I feel like shit everyday of my life, but make it seem as though everything is just dandy.
I love her. I love you all. Boys call me."

event,"Things are doing a little better. I still feel very alone. I don't know what to do. I want to talk to Mitch more than anything in the world right now but I am afraid to call him. We could get in a lot of trouble. I really need to talk to him. Anyhow. I reconnected with Aaron and it's great. I love everyone. Ummm.. yeah. Call me 248 739 1542"

event,"Update: This is a story that I found and thought was funny. It's not about me. I don't have a boyfriend and I don't have a penis.
I'm sitting at home reading when my girlfriend storms in the door after getting back from a dental appointment. She proceeds to stomp up to me and smack me in the head out of the blue.
Her: You made me look like a slut in front of Dr. Bob!
Me: What the hell are you talking about?
Her: I have bruises on the back of my throat from your stupid dick!
Apparently, during the exam, he told her to be careful because she had ""signs of repeated impact trauma to the soft tissue"" or some such medical-speak.
Her: How the hell did I get that?
The Dentist: Um, a blunt object repeatedly striking the back of your throat. [He then turns bright red]"

event,"Today was so crazy. SO much stuff happened and it's just the first day after break. I can't believe that Derek is in the hospital. I hope he will be okay. Everyone says that he will be okay, but still, I duno. I can't imagine falling off the ramp. I heard that he broke his arm most likely and that after he fell, he was unconcious and was seizuring. THat is so scary. I also heard that he landed on his neck. It was crazy today. There were four police officers and they were taking pictures of the ""crime scene"" and stuff. It was weird. Also, today, MIlk and Honey is closed. IT's closed until Wednesday which really bugs me. I wanted to see Nick and I wanted to eat Milk and Honey. Oh well. Umm.. I went to go see Wendy Sadler about my summer job and she completely ignored me. It was so rude. I told Wilma about everything that happened today. I feel bad because usually I only tell her the bad part of my day. Mr. Weiss gave his bible class this special matzah, but it didnt taste any different at all. Everyone just said it to make him feel good. I'm not feeling all that good today. So much has happened. I saw the cutest picture of Katelyn and Mayer. lol. Ummm... I still have to do my bible paper and my math and western civ. I need to find my stickers, it's really important. I talked to Jessi, she's doing well. I miss her so much. She seems to be doing well. I'm in a better mood than usual, I guess. I miss Mitch though so much. He is like the highlight of my life and makes me feel loved and special. I miss him so much. and I love him times bajillion, gazillion, times infinity and beyond. He better call me tonight or I will be sad. I'm really happy that Passover is over. It was too much matzah, lol. Anyways, I'm going to go now. I love you all. Call my cell. 248 739 1542 Ummm... leave me some love."

event,"Ready for more of my pointless babber and self doubt? I think Mitch is going to hook back up with his ex Jill and forget all about me. Just like Justin is with Hilary. Ben won't call me back. Jessi won't answer my calls or call me back period.Aaron thought I died and was hit by a car. I almost did it. But I didn't. I have a deep dark secret that I should probably tell someone, but I don't want to scare them. If I tell someone, I will probably be put away, so I won't tell. It will be my little secret. I feel like I'm going to throw up. There is an all day rehearsal tomorrow. The play is Tuesday through Thursday. We are doing Princess Bride! I ran around so much today, but I also ate a lot. I probably will just end up getting fatter. My left hand has really been bugging me. I mean, it really hurts. I am tired, but not really. I am hot but cold. I feel like being self destructive, but am witholding. I have a cold and a runny nose. It is bugging me. Emma is too. I don't know what to do. I have to go. I love you guys. I'll try to update more often. Emma is being a bitch. Leave me some love. Call my cell. 248.739.1542"

event,"I'm in charge of stage crew and I love it. I could so do this for the next three years. I claim Mitch as mine. I love him so much. I don't really know what to write. Jessi still hasn't contacted me. Her mom's cancer has spread to her legs and her aunt had a stroke. It's really sad. I miss her. I don't really know what to write. Hmmm... Oh well. I'll write more later. I love everyone."

event,"Sadness is bad. I've read everyone else's comments on Elizabeth and it just reassures my feelings towards the situation. Life can just plain suck sometimes. Bad things happen to good people. Good people don't deserve bad things. I love Kiah. I love everyone!"

Today I realized the ultimate consquence of skipping minyan. I can't believe that Elizabeth has cancer. That's not possible. She was fine before. Why would that happen to her? Finding out is so sudden. She was fine! I miss her. She was/is my favorite Toto ever! I wish there was something I could do. This news sucks. Sam was gone for over a month, which sucked! Dr. Cohen in moving to DC in December. Today is my dad's 46th birthday! I finally got my phone back. My dad made rules that I hate. Jessi broke up with me. I'm not allowed to call Mitch, yet. Life isn't all that good right now. I try so hard to do all my homework, but I always seem to miss some. Oh, and plus, I'm fat. Very fat. Life is pretty depressing right now. I like Yellow Raft in Blue Water.
I don't really know what to write about. I'll write later when I get home. Mitch, you can call my from a private line if you want. I love you.

I am obsessed with this manga called Ichigo 100%. It's really good. I like it. I am kind of blah. Tired. I don't know. More than anything in the world... I want my cell phone back. Cut. The blood, the cut. Kiah scratched me. It was beautiful. I want more. MORE! I have to go. Call me if you want. I will be fighting the urge.
Mitch call me when you can or e-mail me."

event,"Last night, Mitch's mom called. She thinks I am suicidal. That is so stupid. I am not. My mom is like then why does she think this then. I'm like I don't know. She's probably crazy. She said that if I didn't let her talk to my parents she would call the Michigan police. Make sense? I didn't think so. I really want to talk to Mitch. I miss him. I miss Jessi and Liv too. I really want to call Mitch. I am definitely hanging out with Jessi this weekend. Sorry, Liv. I just don't have enough time. Maybe while you're on break though. I love you all. I really want to cut. I looked though and I don't have any razors with me. I am going to see Cathy today. I'm not sure I even want to. It's not helping. She just tells my parents things. I really want my cell phone back. I miss it amazingly. Right now nothing is making me happy and I don't know why. I keep triching. I am just blah. Not happy. Not ever happy. I want to be happy more than anything in the world, but I know that it's not going to happen. I don't know what's wrong with me. I'm just not happy. I'm just me. Always will be. I am just me. Nothing I am doing right now is making me happy. I'm not sure if I'll ever be happy again. Nothing ever makes me happy anymore. Well, maybe Kiah does. My friends do too but I'm sad right now. Well, maybe not sad. Maybe numb. Very numb. Yet I can still feel. I feel it all. I don't know what to do. What do I do? Life is not good. It is bad. Not sure. Afraid. Ashamed. Uncomfortable. Hmmm? Why.
I LOVE YOU ALL. DO YOU LOVE ME?"

event,"Talked to Danielle and Marnie today. Fun. I am tired. I don't know what I am doing. I am watching Ripley's Believe It or Not. It is so awesome. I am tired. Life is tiring. I finally finished my Romeo and Juliet stuff. Not really sure what to write about. I feel like cutting. I'm not sure why. I was trying to rub my arms on something. I know that if I cut again, I'll get in really big trouble. I don't know what to do. My trich is acting up. I hate it. The Dr. said something like oh, maybe you can just not pluck as much. I was like yeah right. She knows what trich is, but I don't think she gets it. How could I just stop? It's just like with cutting. I can't just stop. Both are addictions. Addictions that I have been blessed with. jk kind of I don't know. Anyways, love you. Love me. Be love. See love. Give love. LOVE LOVE LOVE

event,"I was trying to be nice, I thought oh well, life sucks, but I'll put on a happy face anyway but that doesn't work. Life sucks. I have to face it. Everything is going so wrong for me right now. Nothing at all is going right. I feel like shit. I want to cut. I really want to. I know it won't help and will just get me in trouble, but as I sit with tears streaming down my face and I don't know what to do. I want to cut. I want to cut. I want to cut. Why can't I? Cutting will make everything feel better. Corrie and Randi and Jessi and I are on the phone and I don't know what to do. What should I do? Want to make me feel better? I feel like shit. Total shit. I don't know what to do. What do I do? I really want to cut. I can't deal with it. Life is terrible. I can't do all this work. I have too much homework and too much other stuff and I can't deal with life and with all that it throws at me. I have homework and everything... I can't do this now. I'll do it later."
event,"Don't read this if you don't want to hear my rant about Dan.

I date Dan, like what 7 months ago? So why should I be upset that he is dating one of my friends? First off, I'd like to congratulate Danielle and Dan on recently getting together. Danielle, I may act bitchy sometimes, but I still love you and it's not you I'm mad at. So anyhow I'm over Dan, but not really. I mean I don't like him anymore, but I don't want to see him dating anyone.

I mean I know I'm dating Jessi, but I duno. I am sad. I can't talk to Mitch anymore. His mom found out and stuff. Anyways, I'm tired. Not in the mood to type anymore. I don't feel safe, cuz his mom might read this and get mad. My mom is home. If you want to know more,  call me,     739 1542.

column1: event,"Today fucking sucked. There is like this guy that though I don't think it's on purpose, he's out to ruin my life.  I mean who tells other guys when they find out that someone is cutting. I mean really. So another guy came up to me today and he said oh show me your muscle. Roll up your sleeves and I'm like no. And I knew he knew so I asked him how he knew and he said Alex told him. I hate Alex. What is his problem? He told both Brads! Then I decided to confront Alex and he said that I was cutting in physics with scissors, which isn't true.  I was just playing with them. I mean still, why do you have to tell everyone?!?! I started crying and it felt so bad. Boys at my school are so mean. So for those of you who don't know the beginning of the story, here goes. Brad came up to me in physics yesterday and he's like do you cut? cuz Alex thinks you're a cutter. I just kind of told him to shove it and left but I felt so bad. Why would he ask for the whole class to hear? If he doesn't want to help me stop, why say anything at all. So today I found out that the other Brad knows. I'm not sure how many people know now. It's not like a secret exactly, I mean people see my scars, but why does he have to announce it to the class and ask if he doesn't really care. Boys are dumb. It's kind of like when this other guy asked across the room in my English class if I was dating Jessica. He yelled across the room! WHY! NO reason. They are so mean. So anyhow I talked with my hebrew teacher and head of school. I was crying and so sad then I had to take a 5 page hebrew test. I'm not really allowed to leave the classroom anymore. Life is so bad right now. I don't know when things will be right again. Any feed back. I told a couple of my friends and they said just ignore it but it's harder to do than that. I called Jessi and my mom and Mitch, but no one answered. NO one at all. Why? I feel so bad. The head of school asked when I last cut. I think he was expecting like a week or two weeks or even a month ago. I felt bad when I told him I had last cut 3-4 days ago. They want to help me but I don't know if I want it. I just want to be left alone and loved."
I'm really pround of myself. I'm going to go return this computer and call Mitch. Mitch I love you. Jessi, I wrote a poem and a song for you. I love you both.
